    "description": "《义军》是《这就是警察》的一款衍生游戏，继承了该系列独特的回合制战术行动。带领一支杂牌警察队伍，反抗镇上的新犯罪势力，看看在你物资匮乏且一枪就能让一个警察丧命的情况下，你能坚持多久。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/8c33dfabd0ba213406ee0599708fb440.poster.avif?t=1725011134\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/8c33dfabd0ba213406ee0599708fb440.webm?t=1725011134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/8c33dfabd0ba213406ee0599708fb440.mp4?t=1725011134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你们虽然不是真正的警察，但你们却是唯一坚守正义的那一方</h2>新登场的施虐狂犯罪头目维克多·苏耶夫很快就让瑞普顿镇陷入了绝境。社区的领导，甚至当地的警察都屈服于他的淫威。作为一个恐吓和敲诈大师，苏耶夫侵占了镇上的每一家大企业，所有这些企业现在都是他自己的私人领地。但有一帮“顽固”的警察拒绝向他低头。他们几乎没有成功的希望，却选择继续战斗——为了正义和这座城镇的灵魂。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/23cb9c0b2176053aedd3d34e11a73589.poster.avif?t=1725011134\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/23cb9c0b2176053aedd3d34e11a73589.webm?t=1725011134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/23cb9c0b2176053aedd3d34e11a73589.mp4?t=1725011134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >枪战令人兴奋，但秘密行动才是取胜的关键</h2>你们在打一场游击战，人手和装备都全面落后。利用隐蔽和掩护，悄悄接近敌人，并在他们能够发出警报之前将其击倒。你有一个非致命武器和装备的军火库，以及一些特殊的战术特技，你可以在升级义军时解锁它们。的确，有时候暴力似乎是在所难免的，但到了那个关头时，便不要有半点犹豫：你和罪犯都没有生命条。当有人被射中时，他会很快因失血过多而死，头部被子弹击中则意味着立即死亡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/7d0f3c5d41e1b204a17dfc88746fd9ce.poster.avif?t=1725011134\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/7d0f3c5d41e1b204a17dfc88746fd9ce.webm?t=1725011134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/7d0f3c5d41e1b204a17dfc88746fd9ce.mp4?t=1725011134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索，搜刮并留意身后</h2>《义军》的特点不仅是紧凑的行动，你需要为每一寸土地战斗，还可以探索大型开放式场所——沙盒关卡。搜查每个房间，打开保险箱和保险库，试着进入禁入的区域——并抢走所有看起来有用的东西。紧密合作，谨慎行事，或者接受风险，四处分散，尝试探索每个角落。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/d878829c566eec5a7eeda0582d9fcea2.poster.avif?t=1725011134\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/d878829c566eec5a7eeda0582d9fcea2.webm?t=1725011134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/d878829c566eec5a7eeda0582d9fcea2.mp4?t=1725011134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高风亮节还是不择手段</h2>苏耶夫的无情是他权力的关键。你能在不按规矩行事的情况下打败他吗？你会满足绝望的市民的需求吗？即使这意味着整个行动将处于危险之中。你会不会放过那些只做本职工作的文职警卫？有人说，在战争中，你必须尽一切努力才能生存，但记住：名誉比金钱更有价值。街上的流氓很容易把你的好名声搞得一团糟。商人会拒绝与你做生意，甚至你自己的一些手下也会背弃你。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/2671899fe24c785f0f9d5a744eb1a443.poster.avif?t=1725011134\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/2671899fe24c785f0f9d5a744eb1a443.webm?t=1725011134\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/970960/extras/2671899fe24c785f0f9d5a744eb1a443.mp4?t=1725011134\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
